text:
I am searching for a woman that I can start an email correspondence which takes the following predetermined path:

1) We email regularly or semi-regularly, and with each email we show greater and greater interest in each other;
2) We discuss meeting, when, where and in what manner, and start to plan something;
3) We engage in some playful sexual talk that arouses both of our interests further;
4) We get closer and closer to the date that we are to meet;
5) You either then a) disappear; or b) postpone to never reschedule; or c) claim a relative died or got sick and you cannot make it; or; d) don't show up.

Then you disappear and all communication ceases and I am left wondering "What the fuck happened here? She was SOOO interested!".

Lets start now!
